{"type":"text","timestamp":1782579047707,"sessionID":"ses_0f608ddeaffeWbGw1R7udtUrQq","part":{"id":"prt_f09fd5608001RPmm6GBa7Ou4pE","messageID":"msg_f09fd3fa6001vsYx2SJ6DNv08Z","sessionID":"ses_0f608ddeaffeWbGw1R7udtUrQq","type":"text","text":"Repaired the scoped `phase-02-startup-session-navigation` source-behavior cluster.\n\n**What I changed**\n- Fixed the test harness blocker by updating shared testability surfaces instead of weakening tests:\n  - `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/onboarding/onboarding_store.cj`\n  - `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/history/history_store.cj`\n  - Added plain-text helpers for onboarding slide labels and history tab labels so tests can verify source text contracts without hitting the current `ResourceStr` generic inference limitation in `std.unittest`.\n- Updated affected tests to use those string helpers while preserving the same behavior checks:\n  - `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj`\n  - `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj`\n- Updated phase-02 authority evidence in `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json` and synced `source-coverage-matrix.md` for the scoped cluster rows that were carrying stale `harness-blocked` evidence:\n  - `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-util-417c58decd-002-navigation-surface-menu-drawer-toolbar-o`\n  - `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-data-repository-lo-02b022d9dd-004-authentication-account-or-session-behavi`\n  - `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-di-appmodule-kt-767a0d2c9a-003-authentication-account-or-session-behavi`\n  - `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-data-repository-ho-76a8c28790-002-data-loading-query-search-filter-or-sort`\n\n**Cluster Sweep**\n- `prep-...-source-behavior-dat`\n  - Verified from source that `FakeData.kt` is seeded in-memory content only.\n  - No phase-02 implementation gap found.\n  - Existing `not-applicable` decision remains correct for file/storage/image/deeplink/permission over-detections in that file.\n- `prep-...-source-behavior-dat-2`\n  - Verified repository behavior parity for fake content reads and persisted login-state toggle.\n  - Replaced stale blocked-test evidence with passing focused-test evidence for representative repository/session rows.\n- `prep-...-source-behavior-di`\n  - Verified source Hilt singleton binding is represented by shared singleton Cangjie services.\n  - Replaced stale blocked-test evidence with passing focused-test evidence for the shared session binding row.\n- `prep-...-source-behavior-dom`\n  - Verified domain contract behavior is already represented by precise target endpoints.\n  - No additional implementation change needed inside phase-02 scope.\n- `prep-...-source-behavior-pre`\n  - Verified route graph, bottom-shell, and cart-action visibility semantics.\n  - Replaced stale blocked-test evidence with passing focused-test evidence for the navigation-shell row.\n\n**Covered Current-Phase Gate Entries**\n- Navigation shell route inventory and bottom-shell visibility contract\n- Persisted login toggle/session routing contract\n- Shared session singleton availability across startup/login/profile flows\n- Full seeded restaurant repository contract\n\n**Remaining Current-Phase Gate Entries**\n- None found in this scoped source-behavior cluster that still required phase-02 implementation work after verification.\n- I did not sweep unrelated clusters beyond this prompt-facing cluster.\n\n**Tests Updated**\n- `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase03_onboarding_login_profile_test.cj`\n- `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj`\n\n**Commands Run**\n- Read scoped brief, plan, protocol, checklist, source files, target files, and repair queue items\n- Reproduced reported test command once:\n  - `cjpm test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` from `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie` with the re